{"tid":1712204,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"防暴警中大射橡膠子彈催淚彈多人傷　有學生疑頭部中彈倒地昏迷","createTime":"2019-11-12T13:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-12T13:41:29.000Z","uid":81228,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"1b9f6feeed06ca5aaf317835e1a439eada5bcec2","tid":1712204,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:40:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111220482452947.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111220482452947.jpeg&h=b95d9eea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大烽煙四起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111220482179324.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111220482179324.jpeg&h=fa0cf5c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有中大生受傷。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111220482099414.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111220482099414.jpeg&h=5fe9b682&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n校園烽煙四起。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111219554196532.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111219554196532.jpeg&h=f1507d5e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大變戰場，火光熊熊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111220482397868.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111220482397868.jpeg&h=c44b3aed&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n火光熊熊。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111220482278644.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111220482278644.jpeg&h=61814075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方晚上再發射催淚彈驅散。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111219554275331.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111219554275331.jpg&h=5ce2ccfc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現場起火冒出濃煙。有線新聞截圖。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111219472895085.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111219472895085.jpeg&h=e7b25040&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田方向有步行往中大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111219472973145.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111219472973145.jpeg&h=b4d42728&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田方向有步行往中大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111219473077329.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111219473077329.jpeg&h=1339026d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沙田方向有步行往中大。<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111220482659295.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111220482659295.jpeg&h=d188da3b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111221190612437.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111221190612437.jpg&h=fa10fc73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111221190836745.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111221190836745.jpg&h=9167cc69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111221190969864.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111221190969864.jpg&h=54fde5af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111221191028390.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111221191028390.jpg&h=2ffcd052&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20191112/_2019111221191122376.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20191112%2F_2019111221191122376.jpg&h=1e688346&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n中大晚上爆發新一輪衝突。中大校長段崇智傍晚與留在中大二號橋範圍的防暴警察談判後，和學生對話，建議學生保證不投擲雜物，警方會退至橋尾。學生要求確認被捕同學情況，校長決定先到警署了解情況，學生一度護送跟隨校長到二號橋尾。在場警方要求黑衣人放下手上電鋸及竹枝，隨即施放催淚彈，黑衣人掟汽油彈還擊。段崇智暫仍未能離開校園。<br />\n<br />\n段崇智一行人及黑衣人行至橋尾，校方要求全部人停下讓校長獨自前往橋尾上車，防暴警察在的橋尾位置舉起藍旗，然後再舉橙旗，要求學生放下武器，不要計畫攻擊警方。警方隨後在距離段崇智50米左右位置發射催淚彈，黑衣人投擲汽油彈還擊，現場起火冒出濃煙。<br />\n<br />\n防暴警與黑衣人對峙，有人築起雨傘陣，警方連續向學生方向發射橡膠子彈，多名學生的眼、胸和腳中槍，有人受傷倒地，現場義務救護員為其進行急救。<br />\n<br />\n有學生懷疑頭部中彈倒地，懷疑失去意識，義務急救員治理，在場人士不斷叫他叫蘇醒，要召喚救護車急救。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1635484/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%84%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7-%E6%9C%89%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E9%A0%AD%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%88%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1635484%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7&d=GxO8KwJzUJLP70ptmK1G7XKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=023e6338\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1635484%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E9%2598%25B2%25E6%259A%25B4%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%25B0%2584%25E6%25A9%25A1%25E8%2586%25A0%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2582%25AC%25E6%25B7%259A%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%25A4%259A%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2582%25B7-%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E7%2594%259F%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%25A0%25AD%25E9%2583%25A8%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25BD%2588%25E5%2580%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E6%2598%258F%25E8%25BF%25B7&h=42f8d106\" target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1635484/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E9%98%B2%E6%9A%B4%E8%AD%A6%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%A7%E5%B0%84%E6%A9%A1%E8%86%A0%E5%AD%90%E5%BD%88%E5%82%AC%E6%B7%9A%E5%BD%88%E5%A4%9A%E4%BA%BA%E5%82%B7-%E6%9C%89%E5%AD%B8%E7%94%9F%E7%96%91%E9%A0%AD%E9%83%A8%E4%B8%AD%E5%BD%88%E5%80%92%E5%9C%B0%E6%98%8F%E8%BF%B7</a>"},{"pid":"f2a0a5c5ab185bd99c15f49ba456bd31be2e6637","tid":1712204,"uid":92038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-12T13:41:29.000Z","msg":"中大學生無示威，係啲警察強行攻入校園，佢地唔係示威者，佢地係學生<br />\nStudents in CUHK did not protest. Instead, HK riot police forcefully attack CUHK. They are students, not protestor. <br />\n#communistmassacre"}]}